            <ul>
                <li><a href="/api/npl">All Data</a> - Get all available data.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/npl/matches">Matches</a> - Get information about all matches.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/npl/matches/:matchNo">Match by Number</a> - Get details of a specific match. (Replace `:matchNo` with match number)</li>
                <li><a href="/api/npl/ranking">Points Table</a> - View the current points table.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/npl/results">Results</a> - Get results of all matches.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/npl/teams">Teams</a> - Get a list of all teams.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/npl/teams/:team">Team by Name</a> - Get details of a specific team. (Replace `:team` with team short form)</li>
